{"tid":2074283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國來中南美洲投資，順便盜獵美洲豹","createTime":"2020-06-22T03:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T04:42:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e82f9a5d7fd7f4e75eaaca0e9458c86bad122a9a","tid":2074283,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"CUP / by Tan Ha Lam<br />\n在中南美洲的美洲豹（Jaguar）近年連環被殺。「紐約時報」引述研究指出，當中國加緊投資開發中南美洲的同時，當地盜獵情況變得更為猖獗。野生動物專家發現，許多美洲豹的交易都與中國公民有關，或是以中國為貿易目的地。例如玻利維亞當局曾截獲送往中國的包裹，裡面就裝有數百隻美洲豹犬齒，預計將會被製作成珠寶。<br />\n<br />\n中國是大型貓科類動物的主要消費國，尤其是老虎，長久以來一直以其骨頭及其他部分，用於傳統醫學，其虎牙及爪則作為珠寶出售。但隨著野生老虎數量減少至只剩下不到 4,000 隻，貿易商轉向以其他來源滿足需求，美洲豹就是其中一種⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/?p=185298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F%3Fp%3D185298&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=f5bd0d5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/?p=185298</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/11/science/jaguars-poaching-china.html?action=click&amp;module=Well&amp;pgtype=Homepage&amp;section=Science\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F06%2F11%2Fscience%2Fjaguars-poaching-china.html%3Faction%3Dclick%26module%3DWell%26pgtype%3DHomepage%26section%3DScience&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=ab2d157b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/11/science/jaguars-poaching-china.html?action=click&amp;module=Well&amp;pgtype=Homepage&amp;section=Science</a>"},{"pid":"cd0b96c50180c99ee61c85eff965bea002114286","tid":2074283,"uid":153151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d07bb87fd72a05294541ac52b2b53b983584e193","tid":2074283,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:54:46.000Z","msg":"象牙都比中國人拆唔少"},{"pid":"8f0088872a4667336eb2f75bab82df0072fc65b3","tid":2074283,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:42:57.000Z","msg":"千年賤種基因真係唔應該現代化"}]}